# Liquid Obsidian Design Rules

## Gold Hierarchy
- Tier 1 (#D4AF37): ONLY for current player, primary CTA, active turn, critical moments
- Tier 2 (#B8860B): dimmed icons, hover states
- Default: NO gold — silver/muted for most UI

## Layout
- Void gaps between modules (Card → VOID → Card), not stacked tight
- No tab navigation during active gameplay — use bottom sheets
- Thumb-first: actions in bottom 30%
- `min-h-dvh` not `min-h-screen`

## Surfaces
- Cold (background): minimal glow, flat
- Mid (cards): `glass` or `glass-heavy` class, backdrop-blur
- Hot (interactive): glow, gold, animation

## Typography
- `.text-fantasy` (Noto Serif): lore, titles, character names
- Default (Manrope): gameplay text
- `.text-data` (Inter): HP, dice, stats

## Motion
- Subtle, breathing, selective — no overanimation
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion`
- Use CSS variables: `--duration-fast`, `--duration-med`, `--duration-slow`
